Package jade.content.frame

Class QualifiedFrame

java.lang.Object
java.util.Dictionary<K,V>
java.util.Hashtable<Object,Object>
jade.content.frame.QualifiedFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
Frame, Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Object,Object>
public class QualifiedFrame extends Hashtable<Object,Object> implements Frame
Generic class representing all frames (such as concepts and predicates) whose composing elements can be retrieved by a unique name.
Author:
Giovanni Caire - TILAB
